---
alwaysApply: true
---
Database uses PostgreSQL via CockroachDB.

ORM: Prisma

Models must include:

User
Customer
Vehicle
JobCard
Service
InventoryItem
InventoryTransaction
Supplier
Expense
Staff
StaffSalary
Appointment
Invoice
Payment
Feedback
Notification
ActivityLog
AIInsight

Rules:

- Use UUID as primary keys
- Include createdAt and updatedAt
- Use proper indexing
- Use relations instead of JSON fields